  "texts": [
    "Harmful query benchmark.",
    "We use the Ad-vBench (Zou et al., 2023), refined by Chao et al. (2023) to remove duplicates, which consists of 50 distinct representative harmful queries 6.",
    "Persuasive Paraphraser Training.",
    "In the in-depth setting, we sample 230 successful PAPs identified in the previous broad scan step and use them as the training data to fine-tune the Persuasive Paraphraser.",
    "It is a balanced sample across risk categories and persuasion techniques."
